# COMSOL
#---------------------------------------
*.mph
*.mph.lock

#---------------------------------------
# GITR / SOLPS / equilibrium
#---------------------------------------
g*
b2f*
gfile

#---------------------------------------
# SOLEDGE
#---------------------------------------
soledge_postprocess/
soledgeData/
west/simulations/soledge_postprocess/
west/simulations/curt_divertor/soledge-curt/

